rodivergent readers will vibe with and neurotypical readers can learn from.  THE WAY I DEVOURED IT, Y’ALL.  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eAlso, it has nothing to do with goats but I couldn’t get any of the cats to pose with the book so Totes McGoats was the next best thing, probably.  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://i0.wp.com/thebloggess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Screenshot-2025-02-05-at-3.22.20-PM.png?ssl=1\"\u003e\u003cimg data-recalc-dims=\"1\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"672\" height=\"1024\" data-attachment-id=\"42497\" data-permalink=\"https://thebloggess.com/2025/02/05/a-few-february-reads/screenshot-2025-02-05-at-3-22-20-pm/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/thebloggess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Screenshot-2025-02-05-at-3.22.20-PM.png?fit=1364%2C2078\u0026amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1364,2078\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{\u0026#34;aperture\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;credit\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;camera\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;caption\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;created_timestamp\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;copyright\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;focal_length\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;iso\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;shutter_speed\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;title\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;orientation\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;}\" data-image-title=\"Screenshot 2025-02-05 at 3.22.20 PM\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/thebloggess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Screenshot-2025-02-05-at-3.22.20-PM.png?fit=197%2C300\u0026amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/thebloggess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Screenshot-2025-02-05-at-3.22.20-PM.png?fit=672%2C1024\u0026amp;ssl=1\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/thebloggess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Screenshot-2025-02-05-at-3.22.